{"tid":1021410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求刺激？男把3條大泥鰍塞肛門　竟順著直腸鑽進肚子","createTime":"2019-02-14T08:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T13:09:25.000Z","uid":75969,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d604e661bfbc111692952d5e39ca10b9803939d","tid":1021410,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/02/14/20190214080250-86d5e60e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F14%2F20190214080250-86d5e60e.jpg&h=ef8181fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸一名男子日前疑似為了尋求刺激，竟將3條大泥鰍塞入肛門裡，沒想到泥鰍順著直腸鑽進肚子裡，無法取出來，他只好前往醫院求助，最後經由手術才成功拿出來。<br />\n<br />\n肝膽外科的羅姓醫師日前在微博分享遇到的病例，一名男子可能為了追求刺激，把3條又肥又長的泥鰍塞入肛門，但泥鰍順著直腸鑽到肚子，讓男子完全拿不出來，只好前往大醫院求救，而透過電腦斷層掃描，可以清楚看到骨盆內有3條細長的魚骨頭，相當驚人！<br />\n<br />\n最後醫師透過剖腹才成功取出來，這3條泥鰍也已經奄奄一息，而羅醫師也嘆說「生活水平梯高，玩法都不一樣了」，更提醒民眾，大家玩歸玩，還是需要把握住尺度。不少網友得知後，也紛紛表示「塞一條可以理解為好玩，三條是不是挑戰極限」、「好噁心，也不怕細菌感染」、「這種死法，泥鰍造了什麼孽」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1082307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F1082307&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=83d583e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1082307</a><br />\n<br />\n闊過西隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d76b29be9dc554db8d68c204d16b923bec62cd1","tid":1021410,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2731df8f38a179ffe8fb03194024756175ea45","tid":1021410,"uid":50526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"男塞3條大泥鰍進肛門「一步到胃」　醫生也傻眼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ckGBxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ckGBxS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9676ff909e91c7415bfabfdbcc5819eb2780576","tid":1021410,"uid":134059,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"「這種死法，泥鰍造了什麼孽」<br />\n<br />\n笑到噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26171d592494d7538c241c0aa1540323231c7a0d","tid":1021410,"uid":195364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"三條係咩玩法"},{"pid":"2bf9327617186b210435ae60c3f5327457553123","tid":1021410,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"又來 係咪咁寂莫呀"},{"pid":"bccd63fcf24d7a789705ba339f751c497d62b535","tid":1021410,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2bf9327617186b210435ae60c3f5327457553123","tid":1021410,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"又來 係咪咁寂莫呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"點解你個名嘅「寂寞」無錯<br />\n留言會錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532ccc5a03a5841105cb4759f43a31649902c57c","tid":1021410,"uid":162644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"又係d死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d930911bce9d570fd0fe86f77a999b477b8103","tid":1021410,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccd63fcf24d7a789705ba339f751c497d62b535","tid":1021410,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2bf9327617186b210435ae60c3f5327457553123","tid":1021410,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"又來 係咪咁寂莫呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"點解你個名嘅「寂寞」無錯<br />\n留言會錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"係喎⋯⋯屌⋯⋯apple個提示字錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2033999e44eb876eb3e31e71c72b0fe2445e3c25","tid":10214